casebody.data:
W. Kevin HUGHES, Chairman, Maryland Public Service Commission, et al., petitioners,
v.
PPL ENERGYPLUS, LLC, et al. No. 14-614. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 19, 2015.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit granted. The case is consolidated and a total of one hour is allotted for oral argument.
